OL,4,Csecret filming of Met police officers
OL,6,FA serving police officer at Charing
OL,7,FCross police officer has been arrested
OL,8,Fon suspicion of perverting the course
OL,9,Fof justice after Metropolitan Police
OL,10,Fofficers were secretly filmed making
OL,11,Fracist and sexist comments.
OL,13,FThe footage, gathered undercover for a
OL,14,FBBC Panorama documentary, appears to
OL,15,Fshow some officers at a central London
OL,16,Fpolice station call for immigrants to
OL,17,Fbe shot and brag about using violence
OL,18,Fagainst suspects.
