OL,4,Csecret filming of Met police officers
OL,6,FNow the Met has confirmed that a
OL,7,Fsergeant attached to the Central West
OL,8,FBasic Command Unit was arrested
OL,9,Ffollowing an "incident" on Thursday
OL,10,FOctober 2, and they had since been
OL,11,Fbailed and suspended from duty.
OL,13,FA force spokesman said: "The
OL,14,Fallegation relates to an incident that
OL,15,Ftook place at Charing Cross Police
OL,16,FStation on 2 October and is linked to
OL,17,Fmatters disclosed in BBC Panorama.
OL,19,F"The investigation is ongoing so it
OL,20,Fwould not be appropriate to go into
OL,21,Ffurther detail at this time.
