OL,6,F"The Independent Office for Police
OL,7,FConduct, which is independently
OL,8,Finvestigating allegations in relation
OL,9,Fto Charing Cross, has been informed."
OL,11,FDeputy Assistant Commissioner Andy
OL,12,FValentine said: "We have been
OL,13,Fextremely clear we will be unrelenting
OL,14,Fin our approach to tackling issues at
OL,15,FCharing Cross, and anywhere else
OL,16,Facross the Met.
