OL,6,F"This fresh matter came to light
OL,7,Fthrough our internal reporting
OL,8,Fmechanisms and we continue to
OL,9,Fencourage and support all our officers
OL,10,Fand staff to report allegations of
OL,11,Fcriminal and conduct behaviour so we
OL,12,Fcan act swiftly.
OL,14,F"Professional standards officers
OL,15,Fimmediately acted to make the arrest
OL,16,Fand the officer has been suspended
OL,17,Ffrom duty.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
