OL,6,F"We will not hesitate to take rapid
OL,7,Faction around any further allegations,
OL,8,Fas part of our deeper probe into
OL,9,Fcorruption and ridding the Met of
OL,10,Fthose who are not fit to serve the
OL,11,Fpeople of London."
OL,13,FReacting to the documentary earlier
OL,14,Fthis week, the Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,15,FStarmer said: "I've not yet seen the
OL,16,Ffootage, but I've had it described to
OL,17,Fme, and it's shocking, and I'm glad
OL,18,Fthe commissioner is responding.
OL,20,F"He needs to be very robust in his
OL,21,Fresponse."
