OL,6,FMet Commissioner Sir Mark Rowley said
OL,7,Fpeople in London could trust the "vast
OL,8,Fmajority" of the force's officers, and
OL,9,Fadded he was "horrified" by the
OL,10,Fdocumentary.
OL,12,FNine serving and one former officer,
OL,13,Fand one designated detention officer
OL,14,Fwho is a civilian member of staff, are
OL,15,Fall under investigation for gross
OL,16,Fmisconduct by watchdog the Independent
OL,17,FOffice for Police Conduct.
OL,26,@oD@bOUpD@IO]qD@NOUqD@XO]
