OL,4,Csecret filming of Met police officers
OL,6,FAllegations include excessive use of
OL,7,Fforce, making discriminatory and
OL,8,Fmisogynistic comments, and failing to
OL,9,Freport or challenge inappropriate
OL,10,Fbehaviour.
OL,12,FOne constable is facing a criminal
OL,13,Finvestigation for allegedly perverting
OL,14,Fthe course of justice.
OL,16,FThe footage shows one officer, Pc Phil
OL,17,FNeilson, referring to an immigrant who
OL,18,Fhad overstayed his visa while off-
OL,19,Fduty, saying: "Either put a bullet
OL,20,Fthrough his head or deport him.
OL,26,@{D@OOU
